State.Name: Water Blending

State.Author: Nikephorros
State.Description: This mod changes the colourful Skyrim Special Edition colours into the original dark Oldrim colours from Legendary Edition. Every single Imagespace from Special Edition has been changed to match the look and feel of Oldrim as close as possible.
State.Name: Epic Oldrim - Original Legendary Colours

State.Author: doodlum
State.Description: Community Shaders feature which replaces grass shaders. Includes a directional light fix, point lights, improved lighting and emulated complex grass.
State.Name: Grass Lighting

State.Author: meh321
State.Description: Stops grass from growing out of rocks, floorboards, bedrolls, crates, roads and other objects. Also allows drawing grass outside of loaded cells.
State.Name: No Grass In Objects

State.Author: Rallyeator
State.Description: Replaces the white foam on water with 4K and optional 2K or 1K textures
State.Name: Rally's Water Foam

State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: Make Riekling barrel traps use SMIM barrels
State.Name: Riekling Barrels SMIM

Original.Name: Hide Quest Items in Container Menu-51243-0-8-1647622538.7z

State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: Hides quest items from the player's inventory when in container menu since you can't put quest items in a container anyways.
State.Name: Hide Quest Items in Container Menu

State.Author: Olivier Doorenbos
State.Description: A script-free total recalibration of Skyrim's detection formula, which improves the balanced and realism of sneaking. Enemies will have enhanced sight and hearing abilities, and will search longer when alerted. Represents over 350 hours of meticulous research and optimization work.
State.Name: Realistic AI Detection (RAID)

State.Author: Expired
State.Description: Adds various custom menus to Skyrim for modder use.
State.Name: UIExtensions

State.Author: ColdTyrant
State.Description: Enables Vampire Lords to talk to NPCs, open doors, pick locks, loot bodies, pick up items, etc.
State.Name: Vampire Lords Can Activate

State.Description: A SKSE plugin that improve the vanilla game combat escape \ stopping mechanism, to prevent you stucking at combat state with super far away enemy.
State.Name: Better Combat Escape - SSE

State.Author: doodlum
State.Description: SKSE plugin which makes local maps use the full screen resolution. Compatible with SE and AE.
State.Name: HD Local Map

State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: Reduce texture seams and pixelation and add collision
State.Name: Blackreach Tentacle Mesh Fix

Original.Name: Move it Dammit - for Skyrim Special Edition v1.1 (Installation Script)-752-1-1-0b.7z

State.Author: E10X11 - Original Mod by Apogee777
State.Description: This is a simple mod that changes a few things real quick to make followers and almost any NPC move back farther than in the vanilla game. The circumstances when this does not happen is if an NPC is "too important" to be moved back.
State.Name: Move it Dammit - for Skyrim Special Edition

State.Author: LegoManIAm94
State.Description: Adds the blur effect on foggy, rainy, snowy and ashstorm weather from Skyrim 2011.
State.Name: Skyrim Distant Blur

State.Author: Quantumyilmaz
State.Description: You dropped your favorited weapon? You ran out of your favorited potion? This mod will automatically favorite them again, once you have them back in your inventory. No esp/scripts. Install/Update/Uninstall whenever.
State.Name: Persistent Favorites

State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: Simple SKSE plugin that allows you to read OR take books
State.Name: Read Or Take SKSE

State.Author: Yuril
State.Description: High Poly ropes, 3D chains support and nails. No ESP
State.Name: FYX - 3D Solitude SighPost

Original.Name: Simplicity of Snow - Blended Roads Patch-59282-1-0-1638262673.7z

State.Author: Titansbane
State.Description: A Simplicity of Snow patch for Blended Roads to properly cover them with snow.
State.Name: Blended Roads - Simplicity of Snow Patch

State.Author: meh321 and z65536
State.Description: Allows to jump while sprinting. Also you can configure jump height multiplier, how many times you can jump (double jump like in action games) . No ESP!
State.Name: Better Jumping SE

State.Author: JaySerpa
State.Description: Rabbits (and other animals) won't walk at the bottom of the sea anymore, they will float near the surface instead.
State.Name: Animals Swim (Sort of)

State.Author: raccoondance
State.Description: NPC's will not use taunts or insults when fighting animals. Especially hunters will behave in a more realistic manner, as well as fixing odd behaviors where enemies wish you a good morning and other unfitting dialogues right after they killed you.
State.Name: Hunters Not Bandits

State.Author: Dovahklon CollinMacleod
State.Description:
Have you ever wonder why the NPCs mostly just stay at the same floor, even though the cell has multiple floors?



This little tweak will encourage NPCs to climb stairs around them and explore their surroundings more.
State.Name: Multiple Floors Sandboxing

State.Author: mindflux
State.Description: The classic particle patch, now on Nexus with enhancements.
State.Name: Particle Patch for ENB

State.Author: Karandra
State.Description: Speeds up game start by storing INI files in memory instead of opening, parsing and closing the file each time some value from it is needed.
State.Name: PrivateProfileRedirector SE - Faster game start (INI file cacher)

State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: SKSE plugin that adds splashes and ripples when raining
State.Name: Splashes of Storms

State.Author: murrayj
State.Description:
Spoiler.



Automatically relights the solitude lighthouse during the quest Lights Out!
State.Name: Lights Out. Solitude Lighthouse Fix

State.Author: uranreactor
State.Description:
Quality of life improvements for the dialogue menu:

Better dialogue controls, number keys to select topics, more topics displayed, configurable list and NPC name position, different skins. 

Ultrawide compatible.
State.Name: Convenient Dialogue UI - SE

State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: SKSE plugin that allows you to favorite books/soul gems/keys and other misc items.

State.Author: Subhuman0100
State.Description: Rewriting many of the vanilla game scripts with the goal of increasing efficiency.  Replacing slower "convenience functions" with their faster native counterparts.    Re-ordering condition checks to implement "fail fast fail early" approach.  Cacheing of often-used values.
State.Name: Vanilla Script (micro)Optimizations

Prevents NPCs from pushing you while YOU'RE WALKIN' 'ERE and having a chat with your friends :)
